attributes.review: I downloaded this app to support my love for Bunker Boy. Unlike everyone else I downloaded the app and it didn’t forever to load it was perfect. I read through the app and then I closed it bc it was 3:00am(keep that in mind). Once I closed out of the app a tv appeared in my room which is odd bc I don’t own any tvs. Fox news hacked into my camera and starting saying horrible things about our non-racists president. I was so angry that I harnessed my eleven powers from stranger things and destroyed the Tv. I said my prayer to Trump like I do every night and fell into a peaceful slumber. At around 5:00am I was RUDLY awoken by Willy Wonka. He told me I was a “bad girl” bc I didn't attend a Back the Blue protest. He then dragged me out of my house a took me to the White House. Jokes on his though I got to see Bunker Boy. Once I saw him I knew something was off. A Cheeto came out and curb stomped me. Then I was forced to do the dishes. Again I didnt mind bc Bunker Boy told me that’s what a women is supposed to do and I love him. Then Michael Jackson came out of a room and kicked me in the ribs. I was sent home to see my dogs were gone and my parents said i was too ugly to be their child. I thought i could move in my Trumpie Poo but he sent me a letter saying “uglie please never🧚🏻‍♀️✨🌈contact me again😘✌🏻💅🏻 love Orange Man💖” I was crushed but I accepted my fate. Now I live inside a tree at Willy Wonka's house. I serve the candy gods now bc bunker boy didn’t want me. If you want bunker boy to reject you download this app or join us. Join the Willies. We are powerful and we have candy!
